commit.title: Check for inductive privacy in make_case_info
commit.message:
Check for inductive privacy in make_case_info

Everyone goes through this since case infos are a pain to build,
except extraction when making a compat body for primitive projections
and kernel/nativecode for the same AFAICT, both of which don't care
about private.
